lead_paragraph: Ryder Cup wildcard Thomas Pieters pulled out of the Dutch Open on Thursday after suffering an allergic reaction to a bee sting.

headline.print_headline: Ryder Cup Wildcard Pieters Out of Dutch Open With Bee Sting
